<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mạ ạ̉bhy̱ ạ̉n njtmʿ ạly̱ ạsm fạdynạ ạlmsyḥ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mā ạảb̊hay̱ ạản̊ naj̊tamiʿa
 ại̹lay̱ ạs̊mi fādīnā ạl̊masīḥ̊
 likaẙ nuqadĩma lahu
 kulã sujūdiⁿ wamadīḥ̊

[V2]
 2- nasẖ̊dū lahu tar̊nīmaẗaⁿ
 tas̊bīḥunā yaḥ̊lū lahu
 nagẖ̊matunā ạl̊mutãḥidah̊
 nab̊gẖī bihā ại̹j̊lạlahu

[V3]
 3- biạl̊qal̊bi nasẖ̊dū biạl̊waqār̊
 nuh̊dī lifādīnā ạltẖãnā
 ại̹dẖ̊ fī ạs̊mihi kulũ ạl̊fakẖār̊
 fī ẓilĩhi yaḥ̊lū ạl̊hanā

[V4]
 4- man̊ gẖaẙrahu ḥāwī ạl̊kamāl̊
 man̊ mitẖ̊luhu bahī̃ ạl̊jamāl̊
 wāfī ạlsãkẖā sāmī ạl̊kẖiṣāl̊
 fīhi lanā kulũ ạlậmāl̊</lyrics>
</song>